{"tid":1503041,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非向撼低新疆燈柱嘅手足致謝。今日嘅operation極之成功。","createTime":"2019-08-24T20:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T04:12:46.000Z","uid":281652,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a7695037c3a832a70afad052fbf9a23a6921d523","tid":1503041,"uid":281652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T20:08:53.000Z","msg":"六月份嘅時份我都仲係<span style=\"color: red;\">教條式和理非</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想講，<span style=\"color: blue;\">我以今日前線伐柱手足為榮</span>。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中共正種族清洗維吾爾人。中共不斷用「曱甴」去形容香港人，<span style=\"color: red;\">係種族清洗嘅伏筆</span>。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不明白「曱甴」點解同種族清洗有關，可以Google Rowanda Genocide同 Nazi Germany嘅歷史。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">撼低新疆燈柱，就係對抗香港新疆化</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日operation成功有幾點：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1) 冷靜的inspect入面嘅electronics，fact-checked and tracked down組件嘅來源，證實個bluetooth system 係幫中共生產監控產品公司做嘅。成件事係一個targeted，specific operation。Force deployment嘅種度低，achieve嘅嘢多，可謂smart power, smart operation嘅極致。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2) 提供大量<span style=\"color: red;\">無法否定嘅證據</span>俾傳媒去打政府，去alarm香港人抵抗監控系統，立刻expose政府由二零一七年至今嘅謊言。新疆燈柱成為主流抗爭議題。<span style=\"color: blue;\">唯一可惜，蘋果無將呢個放上A1，我認為呢個operation，極之成功，媒體應該大報特報。</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3) 長期作戰：今日小試牛刀，<span style=\"color: red;\">但必須想辦法將整個監視系統連根拔起</span>。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後：多謝你冒被捕風險去抵抗新疆化，大家繼續努力，不要放棄。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da5aa194a86cf83fda0d3e4bc32d5eb796179429","tid":1503041,"uid":231342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T20:10:49.000Z","msg":"幫你推下<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Fae8ZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Fae8ZQ.jpg&h=8c6215cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xTx1OZR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxTx1OZR.jpg&h=11d744e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32ec7ccc29e8abfbccd012f733b6015a6999e08f","tid":1503041,"uid":262263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T20:13:27.000Z","msg":"一號波，條柱跣親啫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865eff4211b0fbc41684a862e315da17426b5c68","tid":1503041,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T20:13:35.000Z","msg":"多謝手足們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc9580f2eeda4addf47a773ade1b932b6c660b9","tid":1503041,"uid":281652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da5aa194a86cf83fda0d3e4bc32d5eb796179429","tid":1503041,"uid":231342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T20:10:49.000Z","msg":"幫你推下<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Fae8ZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Fae8ZQ.jpg&h=8c6215cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xTx1OZR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxTx1OZR.jpg&h=11d744e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T20:13:38.000Z","msg":"我地國際文宣真係要重點打cockroaches。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 